I have a code I've been using with 1.5.3.  I want to move to 1.5.4.  I've 
installed 1.5.4 and the examples work fine.  When I compile my code, I get 
the following linking errors.  It seems like it is having problems with the 
pressure regulator and other flow controller devices.  Has this changed 
significantly since 1.5.3?  If so, what do I use instead of PressureRegulator? 
 
make cstr 
g++ -o ./cstr cstr.o -L/usr/local/test/cantera/build/lib/i686-pc-linux-gnu 
-O2 -Wall  \ 
                    -luser -loneD -lzeroD -ltransport -lcantera -lrecipes -lcvode 
-lctlapack -lctmath -lctblas -ltpx -lctcxx
